    <item>
      <title>英伟达超越阿美公司，成为全球第三大最有价值公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/nvidia-leaps-aramco-to-be-world-s-third-most-valuable-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的市值超越沙特阿美公司 (Saudi Aramco)，成为继苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 和微软公司 (Microsoft Corp.) 之后全球第三大最有价值的上市公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/nvidia-leaps-aramco-to-be-world-s-third-most-valuable-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通人工智能辅助现金流模型可减少 90% 的体力劳动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jpmorgan-s-ai-aided-cashflow-model-can-cut-manual-work-by-90</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通Co. 通过其基于人工智能的现金流管理工具帮助其一些企业客户减少了近 90% 的体力工作，使这家美国最大的银行距离这项服务收费又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jpmorgan-s-ai-aided-cashflow-model-can-cut-manual-work-by-90</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
